  ('locality-d592fc58-moex-00058', 'locality-d592fc58', 'locality-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-locality-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設其他條件不變且政府的財政政策與中央銀行的貨幣政策均有效。根據 IS-LM 模型，當政府 減稅且中央銀行賣出債券時，下列敘述何者正確？', '["均衡所得會增加", "均衡所得會減少", "均衡利率會上升", "均衡利率會下降"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "73210569d047", "answer_pdf_sha1": "27b49f81005c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "318", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d592fc58-moex-00059', 'locality-d592fc58', 'locality-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-locality-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '當經濟體系處於流動性陷阱（liquiditytrap）時，下列敘述何者正確？', '["LM曲線呈現垂直線", "寬鬆貨幣政策能降低利率，激勵有效需求，使得所得增加", "經濟已從景氣谷底爬升進入繁榮期", "政府支出增加幾乎不影響利率變化，以致私人投資和消費需求幾乎沒有被排擠，因此，均衡所 得增加幅度很大"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "73210569d047", "answer_pdf_sha1": "27b49f81005c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "318", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d592fc58-moex-00060', 'locality-d592fc58', 'locality-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-locality-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '在小型開放總體經濟體系中，若淨出口（netexports）為負，則下列敘述何者正確？', '["國內支出大於產出", "儲蓄大於投資", "進口小於出口", "淨資本流出為正"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "73210569d047", "answer_pdf_sha1": "27b49f81005c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "318", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d592fc58-moex-00061', 'locality-d592fc58', 'locality-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-locality-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '某一個沒有生產原油的國家，其目前的產出低於充分就業產出。若世界原油價格上漲，根據凱因 斯學派，則該國名目利率將產生下列何種變化？', '["一定下降", "一定上升", "一定不變", "可能上升也可能下降"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "73210569d047", "answer_pdf_sha1": "27b49f81005c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "318", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d592fc58-moex-00062', 'locality-d592fc58', 'locality-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-locality-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據總合供給與總合需求模型的架構，有關總體經濟政策與衝擊對景氣循環影響，下列敘述何者 正確？', '["透過緊縮性貨幣政策讓總合需求線向右移動，以抑制景氣過度擴張的現象", "透過減稅措施刺激消費讓總合需求線向右移動，以避免景氣不佳引起的衰退", "總合供給線會因原物料價格上揚而向右移動，造成產出下滑的景氣收縮變化", "對未來經濟前景樂觀的預期，會讓總合供給線向右移動，帶動景氣擴張變化"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "73210569d047", "answer_pdf_sha1": "27b49f81005c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "318", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d592fc58-moex-00063', 'locality-d592fc58', 'locality-d592fc58-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-locality-d592fc58-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '財政政策中的李嘉圖均等定理（Ricardianequivalencetheorem）無法成立之條件為下列何者？', '["政府課徵定額稅（lump-sumtax）", "人們短視（shortsighted）且非完全理性", "人們能夠跨期規劃", "人們無借貸限制"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "73210569d047", "answer_pdf_sha1": "27b49f81005c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "318", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "商業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
